des: Avocado Toast helps millennials find and cook cheap, healthy, and easy recipes. Currently, the app helps you find substitutes for ingredients you might not have on hand. Soon, the app will help you find and cook recipes that are cheap, healthy, and easy. You don't need to be a trained chef to make some amazing food with Avocado Toast! You'll also be able to count your calories more easily than any other app, so you can stay as healthy as can be. Avocado Toast is food for millennials.
